 <title>PlantNoise - Video</title>
 <link>http://rede.metareciclagem.org/blog/14-09-12/PlantNoise-Video</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;object classid=&quot;D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000&quot; data=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/apps/video/stewart.swf?v=109786&quot; height=&quot;225&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; width=&quot;400&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;flashvars&quot; value=&quot;intl_lang=pt-br&amp;amp;photo_secret=a93cc03e6f&amp;amp;photo_id=7984750498&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/apps/video/stewart.swf?v=109786&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;bgcolor&quot; value=&quot;#000000&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowFullScreen&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;&lt;embed allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#000000&quot; flashvars=&quot;intl_lang=pt-br&amp;amp;photo_secret=a93cc03e6f&amp;amp;photo_id=7984750498&quot; height=&quot;225&quot; src=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/apps/video/stewart.swf?v=109786&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; width=&quot;400&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gerando ru&amp;iacute;dos t&amp;iacute;midos ainda com sensores de capacit&amp;acirc;ncia, toques midis e la&amp;ccedil;os simples no arduino.&lt;/p&gt;
